    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a reliable choice for a daily driver, though it clearly shows its age. The engine and transmission are fully functional and shift as expected, but prospective buyers should plan to replace the brake pads in the near future. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. It has been well-maintained mechanically, but it is no longer in pristine condition.",
