      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The engine starts but suffers from a significant knock and visible fluid leaks, while the transmission exhibits severe slipping between gears. The exterior shows substantial rust on the rocker panels and various dents, and the interior has seen better days with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is sold strictly as-is and will likely require a trailer for transport.",
