    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in wonderful shape! It runs beautifully and has been super well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m really going to miss this one, but I\u2019m excited for it to go to a great new owner. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
