    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle represents an excellent opportunity for a driver seeking a reliable, high-performing car without the showroom price tag. Mechanically, it is in great shape; the engine pulls strong, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and it has been strictly maintained according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though you will find the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light swirl marks that reflect its honest history on the road. Inside, the cabin is clean and inviting. The leather seating is supple with only minor bolster wear on the driver's side, and all electronic features\u2014from the navigation system to the heated seats\u2014are fully operational. It sits on a set of premium tires with significant tread remaining and recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that looks sharp and drives even better, perfect for someone who appreciates quality and value.",
      "price": 32500.0,
